data.description: Spacious Westminster Ranch Home in Linda Park! Home was newly remodeled in 2018.  Kitchen features: stainless steel appliances, updated kitchen cabinets, quartz counter tops, recessed lighting.  Main living room boasts hardwood floors, provides a large living space, the ability to incorporate a formal dining area, easy access to back patio and yard. Hardwoods throughout the main level including hall and bedrooms. Finished basement provides an oversized family/entertainment room with recessed lighting, full bathroom and 2 additional non-conforming bedrooms.  Roof, furnace and water heater are all 5 years old.  Home exterior painted in 2021.  All windows have double pane replacement vinyl windows, basement included. Wide/Long concrete driveway gives ample parking space for 4 cars with additional room for possible RV parking.  Other concrete work includes sidewalk around home to back and patio.  Huge backyard offers plenty of space to create your desired landscape design. Pool table included.  Great location, centrally located to all amenities, restaurants, shopping, public transportation, schools and parks. Buyer Concessions being offered for interest rate buy down!
